          "value": "16"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "kind": "system",
    "body": "SYSTEM FLUSH LOGS query_log",
    "leadingComments": [
      "-- Technically, both SELECT queries have different ASTs, leading to different QC keys. QC does some AST normalization (erase all",
